          "description": "Alison Raemaker was the PA on duty the day I brought my son in due to a sports injury.  She was thorough, kind and efficient during the exam and with all required follow up, i.e. MRI results, finding a physician for continued care.  I am so grateful to have gotten this appointment within 24 hours of his injury and for Alison being so wonderful!",
