          "description": "I had pulled a few muscles in my back or injured a rib. thankfully a friend had told me about HSS Now.  The X-ray service is right there, the reception was sensitive to serving people with mobility and pain problems at intake and the physician I saw was super smart and engaging in figuring out what had happened.  Also they referred me to one of their doctors for follow-up.  Seamless.",
