          "description": "I have taken two of my sons who are athletes to HSS Ortho Injury Care multiple times each. They got x-rays and saw the doc within a couple of days of their injuries. There's nowhere else in the city I know of where you can get an appointment with an ortho that quickly. It's been fantastic.",
