          "description": "Do not go here if your insurance is Medicare or Medicare Advantage. Took my elderly mother there (she has a Cadillac plan as a retired MI state employee ) and just getting an appointment was a nightmare. The billing situation is terribly frustrating because none of the physicians at this practice are credentialed with Medicare. Otherwise the doctors and nurses are nice and seem competent.",
