          "description": "Came in with an sports injury, Dr Robinson made room in the schedule to take me in. The place is very professionally run, no wasted injury. They ordered an X-ray and - with great care and humanity - Dr Robinson went through the options for recovery, distinguishing between non-operative and surgical options and outcomes. The nurse Anne was incredible as well and made sure I had the best fit for the crutches I needed to use.\n\nI super grateful for the team here, especially at such an important moment in life.",
